column5: Haven't posted in a long time due to work getting in the way of fishing...Here's a 48" moonset Muskie that I hooked into this morning......let the fall Muskie hunt begin!!
Nice fish, they seem to be fattening up for the fall a bi early this year.
Awesome fish !!!! I know how you feel.
Very nice yes the moon set was very nice this weekend
Atta boy Steve, great looking fish for sure !!  Sunrise, sunset, moonrise, moonset
Thanks Fellas!!...sure is nice to get back out on the water.
